## Config files

* [auth.ts](mdc:src/lib/auth.ts) is the main config file. We use `auth` only on the server
* [auth-client.ts](mdc:src/lib/auth-client.ts) is the client-side config file. We use `authClient` only on the client.
* [auth-permissions.ts](mdc:src/lib/auth-permissions.ts) is the file that define all the permissions for our application.
* [auth-plans.ts](mdc:src/lib/auth-plans.ts) define the plans of the applications
* [auth-org.ts](mdc:src/lib/auth-org.ts) contain helper for the organization
